title: Techno Ejay 4
description:
Techno eJay 4

RELEASE NOTES

SUPPLIER.....: Joe
CRACKER......: Joe Mamma
PACKAGER.....: Joe Daddy

RELEASE DATE.: 06/26/2003
RELEASE SiZE.: 2 CD
CRACK TYPE...: NONE

Release Type.: APP
OS...........: WinALL

Techno eJay 4 music software with a difference! Techno eJay 4 turns your
PC into the ultimate sound studio with state-of-the-art equipment and
top quality samples. At the same time, Techno eJay is really easy to use
and appealing to the eye. There was never this much in an eJay!

Features

4,000 brand new royalty-free samples
48-track sound studio in CD quality for creative compositions
New! Morphonix virtual synthesizer for making samples from scratch!
Extensive FX Studio including Wave Editor for refining samples
Time&Tune for adapting the tempo of imported sounds
Bass Generator for creating pumping basslines
Polyphonic Hyper Generator synthesizer und sequencer in one with incredible effects
3D VJ Box arrange the visuals to go with your mix
Groove Generator drum computer und 16-track drum sequencer
Improved Recording Studio for laying down vocal samples
CD grabbing for remixes
Voice Generator makes cool voice samples out of texts
Vocoder for robot voice and other sound distortions
Sound import / export in WAVE or MP3 format (import only)
Web connection to the exclusive eJay Online Sound Archive
New graphical interface and full drag & drop support now even more user-friendly

Unrar, burn, enjoy!
